text: Leigh is a small coastal community in the north of Auckland Region, New Zealand and it lies on the western side of Omaha Cove. It is situated 13 kilometers of Matakana, 21 kilometers of Warkworth and 92 kilometers north of Auckland and has a primary school located in the township. ==References== Category:Rodney Local Board Area Category:Settlements in Auckland Region Category:Matakana Coast
title: Leigh, New Zealand
